    "We did not preregister this study.",
    "No information on user demographics such as age, sex, gender or race were collected or determined and -in accordance with the ethics commission -no informed consent by the Twitter users was obtained.",
    "Data collection & final dataset.",
    "We collected tweets from 9th January 2020 to 12th October 2022 using the 1% real-time stream of the Twitter API.",
    "During collection, we filtered the data such that we only gathered tweets containing geo-information from the API."
